cust-backend-2
    description: Multi-system
    product: ProLiant XL170r Gen9 (798155-B21)
    vendor: HP
    serial: SGH550WYYB
    width: 64 bits
    capabilities: smbios-2.8 dmi-2.8 vsyscall32
    configuration: boot=normal chassis=multi-system family=ProLiant sku=798155-B21 uuid=37393831-3535-5347-4835-353057595942

       description: Motherboard
       product: ProLiant XL170r Gen9
       vendor: HP
       physical id: 0
       serial: SGH550WYYB
       slot: Node 1
     *-cache:0
          description: L1 cache
          physical id: 0
          slot: L1-Cache
          size: 512KiB
          capacity: 512KiB

cust-haproxy-be2
    description: Multi-system
    product: ProLiant XL170r Gen9 (798155-B21)
    vendor: HP
    serial: SGH550WJPR
    width: 64 bits
    capabilities: smbios-2.8 dmi-2.8 vsyscall32
    configuration: boot=normal chassis=multi-system family=ProLiant sku=798155-B21 uuid=37393831-3535-5347-4835-3530574A5052
